<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.asafelobotomy.SearchAndDestroy</id>
  <name>xanadOS Search &amp; Destroy</name>
  <summary>Advanced malware detection and system security scanning tool</summary>

  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-3.0-or-later</project_license>

  <description>
    <p>
      xanadOS Search &amp; Destroy is a comprehensive Linux security scanner and system
      protection suite with advanced threat detection capabilities. It provides an
      intuitive PyQt6 interface for ClamAV, RKhunter, and custom security engines.
    </p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time malware scanning with ClamAV integration</li>
      <li>Rootkit detection using RKhunter</li>
      <li>Custom YARA rule-based threat analysis</li>
      <li>System monitoring and file watching</li>
      <li>Quarantine management with secure isolation</li>
      <li>Advanced security reporting and analytics</li>
      <li>GPU-accelerated scanning capabilities</li>
      <li>REST API for automation and integration</li>
      <li>PolicyKit integration for secure privilege escalation</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

